-- =============================================
-- Author:	Vincent Majatladi
-- Create date: 21 August 2014
-- Description: Used for Organisational Scorecard per Dept and SDBIP Scorecard per Department	
-- done this way to keep Columns as Vincent had them so dont have to do an edmx update
